#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.amarok.appdata.xml:20
msgid ""
"Amarok is a free, cross-platform, versatile, powerful and feature-rich music "
"player and collection manager."
msgstr ""
"Amarok je prost program, dostopen na več platformah, vsestranski, močan in s "
"funkcijami nabil predvajalnik glasbe in upravljalnik glasbene zbirke."

